description: Ready to live the quintessential Midtown lifestyle? This stunning 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom condo at ParcVue is coming back to the market with a brand-new price of $289,900. This is your chance to snag a true urban oasis in the heart of Atlanta's most vibrant neighborhood.  Imagine waking up just a few steps from Piedmont Park, then spending your day exploring world-class museums like the High Museum of Art and enjoying top-tier dining and shopping. Everything you need is right at your fingertips, from public transit to corporate offices.  Inside, you'll find a sleek, updated space that's perfect for both relaxing and entertaining. The updated kitchen features solid surface counters and stainless steel appliances, while beautiful hardwood floors flow throughout the main living areas. The spacious living and dining areas open directly onto a large, covered private terrace—the perfect spot to unwind with a drink after a long day. The unit also includes the must-haves: a large closet and in-unit laundry.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a piece of the city. Schedule a tour today and discover your new home!
